INHLANGANO yamazwe ase-Afrika i-African Union imemezele ukuthi izohlola 'ikhambi' le-Covid-19 laseMadagascar njengoba selithengwa emazweni ahluka hlukene kulelizwekazi nakuba iWorld Health Organisation (WHO) ingakakuqinisekisi ukusebenza kwalo. NgoLwesithathu uphini likaSihlalo we-African Union (AU), uMnuz Kwesi Quartey ubhale ekhasini lakhe kuTwitter ukuthi: "ungqongqoshe wezeMpilo eMadagascar usevumile ukusebenzisana ne-African Union ne-Africa Centre for Disease Control ukuhlola ikhambi leCovid-19 abalisebenzisayo ukuze kuhlomule izwekazi lonke."  Excited to update you that, the Republic of #MadagascarCure through its Ministry of Health, has agreed to collaborate with the @_AfricanUnion and @AfricaCDC to explore further, the remedy they have discovered for the treatment of #COVID19 to benefit the continent at large. pic.twitter.com/Uf7SseUL2o